Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.49,0:23:36.40,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\fad(150,100)}信じることが強さに変わる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.49,0:23:39.49,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\fad(150,100)}輝いてよ Shooting STAR

